<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 06:20:53 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>Nio 与 Monolith 合作进行实时人工智能电动汽车电池测试</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/nio-partners-with-monolith-real-time-ai-ev-battery-testing-2024-10-01/</link><description>蔚来汽车周二表示，该公司正在与英国人工智能软件初创公司 Monolith 合作，利用这家中国电动汽车制造商在欧洲的电池更换服务来实时测试和改进电动汽车电池组。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 06:03:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/artificial-intelligence/nio-partners-with-monolith-real-time-ai-ev-battery-testing-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体报道，中国军队在南海部分地区进行巡逻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-military-conducts-patrols-parts-south-china-sea-state-media-2024-10-01/</link><description>据中国官方媒体报道，中国军队周一至周二在南海部分地区进行了战备巡逻，这是周末在该地区罕见的军事演习和演习的延伸。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 04:49:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinese-military-conducts-patrols-parts-south-china-sea-state-media-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>媒体报道，越南渔船在有争议的南海岛屿附近遭到袭击</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-fishing-boat-attacked-near-contested-south-china-sea-islands-media-2024-10-01/</link><description>据官方媒体周一晚间报道，至少 10 名越南渔民在中国和越南均声称拥有主权的西沙群岛附近捕鱼时遭到外国船只袭击，造成至少 10 名越南渔民受伤。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 03:01:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-fishing-boat-attacked-near-contested-south-china-sea-islands-media-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>如果中国克服真菌担忧，澳大利亚可能成为油菜籽贸易赢家</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/australia-could-be-canola-trade-winner-if-china-gets-over-fungus-worries-2024-10-01/</link><description>如果中国对加拿大进口的油籽征收关税，澳大利亚可能会成为全球油菜籽贸易流向转变的赢家，但北京方面需要克服他们对真菌的担忧。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 02:44:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/australia-could-be-canola-trade-winner-if-china-gets-over-fungus-worries-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>台湾警告强台风“克拉通”带来的风暴潮并动员军队</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/troops-mobilised-taiwan-warns-storm-surge-powerful-typhoon-krathon-2024-10-01/</link><description>周二，强大的台风“克拉松”逼近人口稠密的西南海岸，台湾动员了近 4 万名士兵，随时准备开展救援工作，该地区正面临风暴潮。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 02:28:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/troops-mobilised-taiwan-warns-storm-surge-powerful-typhoon-krathon-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>亚洲工厂活动受到全球不确定性打击，关注中国刺激措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-economy-asias-factory-activity-hit-by-global-uncertainty-focus-china-2024-10-01/</link><description>私营部门调查显示，由于中国需求疲软和全球经济不确定性预示着前景充满挑战，亚洲 9 月份工厂活动减弱，使政策制定者面临支撑脆弱增长的压力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 02:15:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-economy-asias-factory-activity-hit-by-global-uncertainty-focus-china-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>交易员考虑美国利率，亚洲股市波动，美元坚挺</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-10-01/</link><description>周二，亚洲股市从两年半高点回落，美元走强，此前美联储主席鲍威尔发表言论，大幅降息的押注落空，而中东紧张局势则抑制了风险情绪。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 02:10:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>国庆前夕，上海发生持刀袭击事件，造成三人死亡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/shanghai-knife-attack-kills-three-wounds-15-others-xinhua-reports-2024-10-01/</link><description>周一，中国国庆节假期前夕，上海郊区一家超市发生持刀袭击事件，造成 3 人死亡、15 人受伤，这是今年中国主要城市发生的一系列持刀伤人事件中的最新一起。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 01:52:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/shanghai-knife-attack-kills-three-wounds-15-others-xinhua-reports-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>海地冲突导致数千人陷入饥荒</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/haiti-conflict-drives-thousands-toward-famine-2024-10-01/</link><description>近几个月来，海地因帮派引发的社会和政治危机导致遭受严重饥饿的人数不断增加，估计有 540 万海地人已经耗尽了食物，并且一天或更长时间没有进食。</description><pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 00:54:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/haiti-conflict-drives-thousands-toward-famine-2024-10-01/</guid></item><item><title>全球投资者呼吁撤离中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-investors-call-time-their-exodus-china-2024-09-30/</link><description>全球投资者正准备再次押注中国，这是北京努力扭转经济放缓并重振股市长期兴趣引发的重大情绪转变。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 23:06:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-investors-call-time-their-exodus-china-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>美国轰炸机将参加韩国阅兵引发朝鲜愤怒</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-criticises-us-deployment-nuclear-assets-south-korea-2024-09-30/</link><description>韩国将于周二在首尔举行阅兵式，其中可能包括首次由美国 B-1B 超音速轰炸机进行飞行表演，因为邻国朝鲜批评美国在朝鲜半岛部署军事资产。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 22:23:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-criticises-us-deployment-nuclear-assets-south-korea-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞标：鲍威尔慎重，中国为第四季度开盘奠定了基础</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-09-30/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 21:47:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-pix-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>马赫雷斯进球让阿赫利在亚冠联赛中保持完美</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/mahrez-strikes-keep-al-ahli-perfect-asian-champions-league-2024-09-30/</link><description>沙特阿拉伯的阿赫利队周一在亚洲冠军联赛精英赛中保持了完美的开局，里亚德·马赫雷斯和罗杰·伊巴内斯的进球帮助球队以 2-0 战胜了阿尔瓦斯尔队，而克里斯蒂亚诺·罗纳尔多则在阿尔纳赛尔队以 2-1 战胜阿尔-瓦斯尔队的比赛中进球。雷扬。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 20:55:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/mahrez-strikes-keep-al-ahli-perfect-asian-champions-league-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国的激励措施吸引了谨慎的电动汽车买家，特斯拉的季度交付量将上升</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-quarterly-deliveries-set-rise-china-incentives-lure-wary-ev-buyers-2024-09-30/</link><description>华尔街估计，在全球最大汽车市场中国的长期激励措施和利润丰厚的融资计划的推动下，特斯拉周三第三季度电动汽车交付量预计将增长 8%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 17:30:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-quarterly-deliveries-set-rise-china-incentives-lure-wary-ev-buyers-2024-09-30/</guid></item><item><title>科学家解释珠穆朗玛峰的异常生长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/science/scientists-explain-mount-everests-anomalous-growth-2024-09-30/</link><description>珠穆朗玛峰是地球上最高的山峰，海拔 8.85 公里（5.5 英里），而且实际上还在不断增长。</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 17:05:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/science/scientists-explain-mount-everests-anomalous-growth-2024-09-30/</guid></item></channel></rss>